# Browser History App

## Project Description

The Browser History App is a React application that displays a list of browser history items. Users can search history entries using a search bar and delete individual history items. The application updates dynamically based on user interactions.

## Features

- Display browser history items.
- Search history items irrespective of letter case.
- Delete individual history entries.
- Show Empty History View when no matching records are found.
- Show Empty History View when all history items are deleted.

## React Concepts Used

- Class Components
- State Management
- Event Handling
- Conditional Rendering
- List Rendering using map()
- Filtering Arrays
- Props

