## Component Structure

### BrowserHistory Component

Responsibilities:
- Stores history list in state.
- Handles search functionality.
- Filters history items.
- Deletes history items.
- Displays Empty History View when required.

### HistoryItem Component

Responsibilities:
- Displays a single history item.
- Displays logo, title, domain URL, and time accessed.
- Provides delete button functionality.

## State Variables

- searchInput
- historyList

## Methods Implemented

### onChangeSearchInput()
Updates search input value.

### deleteHistoryItem()
Removes selected history item from history list.

